  "_comment": "THE INPUT MAP AS ROWS — every verb is an action with KEY and PAD bindings (edit here or in the in-game CONTROLS panel; user://input_overrides.json wins). Descriptors: key:<NAME> (Godot key name: E, SHIFT, CTRL, SPACE, TAB, F5, KP_1…) · mouse:left/right/middle · joy:a/b/x/y/lb/rb/l3/r3/start/back/dpad_up/dpad_down/dpad_left/dpad_right · axis:rt/lt (triggers) · axis:lx/ly/rx/ry:+/- (stick directions). PS2-family pads read the same rows (cross=a, circle=b, square=x, triangle=y). Existing engine actions (move_*, jump, interact) keep their ids — rows here EXTEND them with pad events and let the panel rebind their keys.",
